Cocos2D Projects written for Steffen Itterheim's bi-weekly iDevBlogADay post.

Visit Steffen's Learn Cocos2D websites:
http://www.learn-cocos2d.com (blog & store)
http://www.learn-cocos2d.com/tag/idevblogaday/ (list of iDevBlogADay posts)
http://www.kobold2d.com (an improved Cocos2D)


This is an Xcode 4 workspace containing multiple Cocos2D projects. Every time I write a new iDevBlogADay post that includes a source code project, I'll add it to this repository. Occasionally I may even update the source code to include new features not covered by the original blog post. 

Note that each project works independently from the Xcode workspace as well.


